N="207 bk." UNIT="leaf">
whi hase &thorn;ou lefte me &thorn;us.'  The fyfte was, `Scicio,'
&thorn;at es to say, `I haf thriste.'  The sexte worde was this, `In
manus tuas Domine, &amp;c'.' whilke es for to saye, `Fadir, in-to &thorn;i
haundis I gyffe my sawle.'  The Seuen&dtail; worde was &thorn;is,
