&THORN;e thirde thynge es gastely, &thorn;e grace &thorn;at we
rescheyue whe&ntail; we take &thorn;at flesche and &thorn;at blude.
We se &thorn;are lyknes of brede and of wyne, and it es noghte; bot we
trowe &thorn;at &thorn;are es sothefastly &thorn;e flesche and
&thorn;e blude of Ihesu Criste.  And noghte forthi &thorn;e lyknes of
flesche ne may we noghte see.  And &thorn;are-fore, &thorn;are whare
