<PB N="62">


&thorn;e fylthe, and ordayned it, and restorede better &thorn;a&ntail;
it was by-fore.  Now I pray &yogh;ow a&llbar; in charite of God,
&thorn;at a&llbar; &thorn;a &thorn;at of this relegio&ntail; redis or
heris, &thorn;at &thorn;ay be bouxome with a&llbar; &thorn;aire
myghte, and suffire &thorn;at &thorn;e gud ladys be-fore namede do
&thorn;aire offece ilke daye gastely with-in &thorn;aire hertes.  And
luke ylkone wysely &thorn;at he ne do no trispase agayne &thorn;e
rewle ne &thorn;e obedyence of &thorn;is relegio&ntail;, and of
&thorn;ase lufe-frayners.  And if thorow vnhape fa&llbar;e &thorn;at
any of thiese foure fendis doghetirs seke one any wyse any Ingate for
to hafe with-in &yogh;oure hertes for to due&llbar;e, or Ingate hase
wonne, and with &yogh;ow duellis, do so, after &thorn;e conce&llbar;e
of &thorn;e lady Discrescio&ntail;, and gyffe &yogh;ow to
deuocio&ntail; with hertly prayers, in hope of Goddes helpe and of his
socoure, and &yogh;e sa&llbar; be delyuerde thurgh &thorn;e mercy of
oure Lord Ihesu Criste there.  Blyssede mot he he with-owtte&ntail;
ende! Ame&ntail;</P>

<TRAILER>Explicit Relegio Sancti Spiritus.  Ame&ntail;.</TRAILER>
